contentDescriptions.description: A women's panty set designed specifically for the hijab clothing collection, offering comfort and elegance together. Thanks to its buttoned closure, it can be easily put on and taken off, making it suitable for daily use.

a simple and elegant appearance is achieved with its flat pattern, it can be combined with any accessory. Thanks to its regular fit, it offers an ideal fit that wraps around the body lines but does not tighten.

while creating a modern and casual style with a bicycle collar, the combination of shirt-pants is both a stylish and practical option.This suit, which comes as a set of 2 pieces, allows you to easily find the complementary pieces. The design, which appeals to the age range from 21 to 40, is preferred by women with young and dynamic styles. It offers comfortable use while giving a soft touch feeling with its 50% viscose, 45% polyester and 5% lycra content. It provides a comfortable feeling by adapting to different body types with its standard height size.
the pants with elastic waist detail offer a comfortable experience with a steady posture all day long.

thanks to the high waist design, it helps to create a modern and elegant silhouette while also gently wrapping the body lines.With its pipe leg cut, it displays a classic and timeless style while also allowing for comfortable movement. The long arm length is integrated with the standard mold, providing ideal usage opportunity during seasonal transitions. Thanks to its straight silhouette, it adapts to your sense of trendy style while displaying a neat and stylish stance.

With its brown tone, it offers easy combinability while giving it a sophisticated look in any setting. The woven fabric type promises long-term use by increasing durability, while its moderate thickness provides ideal comfort during seasonal transitions.
